Name: Lucky VS Aliens
About the game: Play for the penguin, who must protect his cows from UFOs! Do not let the aliens pick up their cows and hit the flying saucer with dynamite and a built catapult! You have to move fast, shoot a lot, and throw explosives at an alien ship in order to protect your small farm. Features: - Fun and fast gameplay - Primary and secondary weapons - Nice, stylized graphics - New gaming experience - Earn points and open additional weapons
